parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while accelerating, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Horn failure can reduce the ability to alert other drivers or pedestrians, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Exhaust odor can cause health problems or discomfort for occupants.
